  "description": "Semi-Vanilla ∙ Enjoy the game how it's meant to be played. 100+ Mods, New Structures, Dungeons and much more!",
  "body": "![Header](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/f1b0eb1e4ade83e6730cd90a29641df539910a81.png)\n\n<b>Enjoy the game how it's meant to be played with New World Generations, Storage Solutions and many more mods!</b>\n\n### Disclaimer:  \nMake sure you backup your World, Configs, Server BEFORE You update to a newer version of this Modpack  \n\n⭐ — Overhauled World Generation (Biomes o' Plenty, Regions Unexplored & Formations)  \n⭐ — Overhauled Strongholds, Monuments & Nether Fortresses  \n⭐ — New Dungeons to Explore (Rougelike Dungeons & Dungeon Crawl)  \n⭐ — QoL Improvements with Waystones & XP Tomes  \n⭐ — New Storage Solutions (Iron Chests, Refined Storage)\n\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/8Xhhz4O.png\" alt=\"Better Line Break\">\n\n### For Server Hosting - [IMPORTANT]\nTo make sure you have no issues when hosting this modpack on your server, you'll need to remove some of these mods to make your server run properly. _(I'll be working on a Server Version once I get configs tweaked)_\n\nMods to Remove:  \n❌ — Oculus  \n❌ — YUNG's Menu Tweaks\n\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/8Xhhz4O.png\" alt=\"Better Line Break\">\n\n&nbsp;\n&nbsp;\n<details>\n  <summary>Mods Included (117)</summary>\n  <ul>\n    <li>🟢 <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/aeroblender\" target=\"_blank\">AeroBlender</a></li>\n    <li>🟢 <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/aether-protect-your-moa\" target=\"_blank\">Aether Addon: Protect Your Moa</a></li>\n    <li>🟢 <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/alexs-mobs\" target=\"_blank\">Alex's Mobs</a></li>\n    <li>🟢 <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/ancient-aether\" target=\"_blank\">Ancient Aether</a></li>\n    <li>🟢 <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/another-furniture\" target=\"_blank\">Another Furniture</a></li>\n    <li>🟢 <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/architectury-api\" target=\"_blank\">Architectury API\n</a></li>\n    <li>🟢 <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/azurelib\" target=\"_blank\">AzureLib\n</a></li>\n    <li>🟢 <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/bclib\" target=\"_blank\">BCLib\n</a></li>\n    <li>🟢 <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/balm\" target=\"_blank\">Balm\n</a></li>\n    <li>🟢 <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/better-advancements\" target=\"_blank\">Better Advancements\n</a></li>\n    <li>🟢 <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/better-compatibility-checker\" target=\"_blank\">Better Compatibility Checker\n</a></li>\n    <li>🟢 <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/betterend\" target=\"_blank\">BetterEnd\n</a></li>\n    <li>🟠 <a href=\"https://curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/better-end-crashed-ships-tweaks\" target=\"_blank\">BetterEnd Crashed Ships\n</a></li>\n    <li>🟢 <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/betternether\" target=\"_blank\">BetterNether\n</a></li>\n    <li>🟢 <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/biomes-o-plenty\" target=\"_blank\">Biomes O' Plenty\n</a></li>\n    <li>🟢 <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/bountiful\" target=\"_blank\">Bountiful\n</a></li>\n    <li>🟢 <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/bygone-nether\" target=\"_blank\">Bygone Nether\n</a></li>\n    <li>🟢 <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cc-tweaked\" target=\"_blank\">CC: Tweaked\n</a></li>\n    <li>🟢 <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/caelus\" target=\"_blank\">Caelus API\n</a></li>\n    <li>🟢 <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/chat-heads\" target=\"_blank\">Chat Heads\n</a></li>\n    <li>🟢 <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/chefs-delight\" target=\"_blank\">Chef's Delight\n</a></li>\n    <li>🟢 <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/citadel\" target=\"_blank\">Citadel\n</a></li>\n    <li>🟢 <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cloth-config\" target=\"_blank\">Cloth Config API\n</a></li>\n    <li>🟢 <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/forgified-fabric-api\" target=\"_blank\">Forgified Fabric API\n</a></li>\n    <li>🟢 <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/connector\" target=\"_blank\">Sinytra Connector\n</a></li>\n    <li>🟢 <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/connector-extras\" target=\"_blank\">Connector Extras\n</a></li>\n   